trans-unit.source: Specifies the kind of border that surrounds a Web Parts control.
trans-unit.target: Angir hva slags kantlinje som omgir en webdeler-kontroll.

trans-unit.source: A part control's PartChromeType enumeration determines what kind of border surrounds a Web Parts control.
trans-unit.target: Del kontrollens PartChromeType opplisting bestemmer hvilken type kantlinje omgir en webdeler-kontroll.

trans-unit.source: Options include showing a title bar only, a border only, a title bar and border, or neither.
trans-unit.target: Alternativene er viser en tittellinjen bare, bare en kantlinje, en tittellinjen og kantlinjen eller ingen.

trans-unit.source: If the enumeration value is set to Default on the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.Part.ChromeType%2A> property of a part control, the control inherits its setting from the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebZone.PartChromeType%2A> property of the zone that contains the control.
trans-unit.target: Hvis opplistingsverdien er satt til standard p√• den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.Part.ChromeType%2A>egenskapen til en kontroll som en del kontrollen arver egenskapsinnstillingen fra den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebZone.PartChromeType%2A>for sonen som inneholder kontrollen.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebZone.PartChromeType%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.Part.ChromeType%2A>

trans-unit.source: A border only, without a title bar.
A border setting inherited from the part control's containing zone.
trans-unit.target: En kantlinje innstillingen arvet fra en del-kontroll for som inneholder sone.

trans-unit.source: No border and no title bar.
A title bar and a border.
A title bar only, without a border.
